name: NIGHT POUR HOMME II + III 100ML / 3.38 oz
details: ZARA NIGHT POUR HOMME II + ZARA NIGHT POUR HOMME III EAU DE PARFUM 2X100ML (3.4 FL. OZ).A collection of fragrances to give the finishing touch to your outfit, whether elegant, sophisticated or bold. Providing a dark and intoxicating touch at night, and during the day unveiling lively and magnetic notes.NIGHT POUR HOMME II, a modern oriental fougère where seductive and warm spices are intermingled with notes of dry woods for an intoxicating trail. The fragrance pyramid reveals fruity notes of bergamot, grapefruit and lemon wrapped in cardamom, lavender and nutmeg. In the background we find musky and vanilla notes accompanied by cedar wood, amber and tonka bean. A provocative fragrance for the man who defends his carefree personality.NIGHT POUR HOMME III, a woody fragrance that reveals an elegant and fresh character with an iridescent floral explosion. The fragrance pyramid reveals fruity notes of bergamot and pear, wrapped in iris, osmanthus, coriander and pepper. In the background we find woody notes of sandalwood and cashmere accompanied by leather and vetiver notes. A unique, seductive and irresistible trail.View more

name: RED TEMPTATION 80 ML / 2.71 oz
details: ZARA RED TEMPTATION EDP 80 ML (2.71 FL. OZ). Eau de parfum disguised as the warm and textured facets of beautiful Saffron and coriander spices; bitter orange lends a fruity and colourful touch to the luminous floral bouquet. The luminosity of jasmine reveals all the sensuality and femininity of white flowers, enhanced by a praline, modern and ultra-addictive accord. The flowers are highlighted by the power of moss and woody amber notes, enveloped in a cloud of musk, leaving a trail of complete femininity.View more

It is all there to decorate and enhance a rose with modern freshness and strong character. Far from embodying innocence and purity, it bestows and incites an unstoppable wave of feminine empowerment, providing pure delight that every woman has a right to. Soft, delicious and creamy gourmand caramel notes blend with a lively and nostalgic vanilla aroma, with a trail of amber musk that affirms the ultimate power of the rose.View more

name: AMBER FUSION 80 ML / 2.71 oz
details: ZARA AMBER FUSION EDP 80 ML (2.71 FL. OZ). Eau de parfum in which citrus freshness of bergamot and tangerine are mixed with sea-inspired notes for a stunning introduction and cheerful fluidly, which plays to prolong with the colourful hints and acids of red berries. At the heart, the floral and crystalline delicacy of lily contrasts with the floral value of sunny and captivating ylang-ylang.
